channel.description: Anyone got a NPC ID list? I spawned a NPC from 100000s... and I was curious where it ended because I needed empty IDs to add my GWD NPCs. When I tried to write over them, it doesn't work and was told I needed empty IDs.

item.title: [PI] Does anyone have a PI NPC ID list?
item.dc:creator: @PServ123 PServ123
item.description:
@PServ123 wrote:

I am using the original PI. I uncommented the GWD NPCs that were already in it and it worked fine, but when I changed the IDs, they started to not work. I asked around for the reason and was told that I couldn’t write over an NPC. So I tried to go further down the list and I did 100k… and it was an NPC, so I don’t know where to put them…
